==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Imbody
<hw>Im*bod"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Embody</er>.]</ety> <def>To become corporeal; to assume the
qualities of a material body. See <er>Embody</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The soul grows clotted by contagion,⟦br⟧
<qex>Imbodies</qex>, and imbrutes.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Imboil</ent>⟦br⟧
